{"tid":424743,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"地產Smart Lady：Mini有個3年換樓大計","createTime":"2017-10-05T04:55:00.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-23T06:38:45.000Z","uid":81228,"like":1,"dislike":12,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"869d974f1bdd935a1f0bbf1c465c76a939615582","tid":424743,"uid":81228,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-05T04:55:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/finance/20171005/photo/bkn-20171005111607631-1005_00842_001_01b.jpg?20171005123802\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Ffinance%2F20171005%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20171005111607631-1005_00842_001_01b.jpg%3F20171005123802&h=69fe3515&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/finance/20171005/photo/bkn-20171005111607631-1005_00842_001_02b.jpg?20171005123802\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Ffinance%2F20171005%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20171005111607631-1005_00842_001_02b.jpg%3F20171005123802&h=31e09c3d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/finance/20171005/photo/bkn-20171005111607631-1005_00842_001_03b.jpg?20171005123802\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Ffinance%2F20171005%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20171005111607631-1005_00842_001_03b.jpg%3F20171005123802&h=b0c5f91a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/finance/20171005/photo/bkn-20171005111607631-1005_00842_001_04b.jpg?20171005123802\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Ffinance%2F20171005%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20171005111607631-1005_00842_001_04b.jpg%3F20171005123802&h=81ddce6d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/finance/20171005/photo/bkn-20171005111607631-1005_00842_001_05b.jpg?20171005123802\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Ffinance%2F20171005%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20171005111607631-1005_00842_001_05b.jpg%3F20171005123802&h=00f8ab4a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/finance/20171005/photo/bkn-20171005111607631-1005_00842_001_06b.jpg?20171005123802\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Ffinance%2F20171005%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20171005111607631-1005_00842_001_06b.jpg%3F20171005123802&h=58e60262&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/finance/20171005/photo/bkn-20171005111607631-1005_00842_001_07b.jpg?20171005123802\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Ffinance%2F20171005%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20171005111607631-1005_00842_001_07b.jpg%3F20171005123802&h=d9c36745&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/finance/20171005/photo/bkn-20171005111607631-1005_00842_001_08b.jpg?20171005123802\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Ffinance%2F20171005%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20171005111607631-1005_00842_001_08b.jpg%3F20171005123802&h=3ad66c8c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/finance/20171005/photo/bkn-20171005111607631-1005_00842_001_09b.jpg?20171005123802\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Ffinance%2F20171005%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20171005111607631-1005_00842_001_09b.jpg%3F20171005123802&h=bbf309ab&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n香港地上車甚困難，對時下80、90後年輕人而言，放棄娛樂是否上車的唯一出路呢？今期「地產Smart Lady」主角Mini入行雖然短短7年，為了做「孝順女」助家人提升生活質素，同時為自己打造安樂窩，憑着個人努力，成功在3年內連掃兩層樓。<br />\n<br />\n性格爽朗、樣子甜美的Mini，現時任職香港置業客戶經理，幾年前從金融業轉投地產界，經朋友介紹下入行。起初她對地產一無所知，平時要熟讀樓盤資料及區內成交，「好多嘢膽粗粗去嘗試。」<br />\n<br />\n作為代理，熟悉樓市自然享近水樓台之利，Mini在2014年樓價仍相對低水時，看準入市時機，聯同家人合力斥資逾百萬元作首期，買入天水圍區內私樓1個單位，現時予家人居住。其後，Mini食髓知味睇好後市，至今年8月初時再度入市，今次更獨力一人斥約90萬元作兩成首期，購買葵涌新盤1個細單位，有待入伙後作自住之用。<br />\n<br />\n年紀輕輕，Mini坐擁兩層物業固然開心，但同時間亦要面對巨大的供款壓力，她坦言，現時每月供樓的支出佔其收入的一半，「供樓其實都吃力，但好彩本身自己有做長線投資，另外亦要勤力啲開單，再將佣金的8成儲起，作為供樓基金」。<br />\n<br />\n「升呢」做業主之後，Mini化身「慳妹」，「依家慳咗好多，未上車之前，一年會去4至5次旅行，但家陣最多都係去兩次，其他無謂消費唔會再付出」。拒絕及時行樂的心態，Mini認為「人一定要有自己的空間，況且租樓費用昂貴，等同幫人供樓，有能力當然係自己供樓最好」。<br />\n<br />\nMini眼界更不止僅僅手持兩層物業，從小鍾情地方較大的特色單位或洋房，她更計劃3年內以「樓換樓」形式買入屬於自己的Dream House。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/finance/20171005/bkn-20171005111607631-1005_00842_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Ffinance%2F20171005%2Fbkn-20171005111607631-1005_00842_001.html&d=qm%2FEjCb%2BruC%2FKbOXS6utqJWUQYxlHU4vp7GM3pu%2FB4U%3D&h=05615f01\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/finance/20171005/bkn-20171005111607631-1005_00842_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"831281bfdf384d2fba9d0b59154d1a3998a9b5be","tid":424743,"uid":40470,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-05T05:01:35.000Z","msg":"個樣好似會突然咬死你咁"},{"pid":"f6f05e3755aca32d3ba03f26e80f238dbe6b6f59","tid":424743,"uid":19676,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-05T05:02:41.000Z","msg":"吹撚到<br />\n<br />\n你做地產點供兩層樓？"},{"pid":"aec61a310aec1154956bfa71f9b53ae6e0bd2313","tid":424743,"uid":49588,"like":12,"dislike":1,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-05T05:09:02.000Z","msg":"始終女人有「八達通」，喺唔同D！"},{"pid":"dc1924409d4acaf0f797d80465fb70220a728edd","tid":424743,"uid":121409,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-05T05:11:32.000Z","msg":"塊面咩左<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6756dd32a2a14d6f19c129415a526fd4f1c4eb26","tid":424743,"uid":93986,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-05T07:29:39.000Z","msg":"女人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fbca9fa070c6e4a24cb60a19dc2fdb4abaadbe15","tid":424743,"uid":149855,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-05T16:42:58.000Z","msg":"請唔請男朋友<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"916ec958a17460cea0d3b96480b80a493d5dca3c","tid":424743,"uid":38820,"lik